<div id="review_139712323" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/139712323" />
    <a title="Scarlet" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4684496-scarlet"><img alt="Scarlet" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1355253003p2/4684496.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/139712323?book_show_action=true">Jan 10, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Scarlet" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Scarlet" href="/user/show/4684496-scarlet">Scarlet</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">noone</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4684496-scarlet?shelf=angels">angels</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4684496-scarlet?shelf=demon">demon</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4684496-scarlet?shelf=paranormal-romance">paranormal-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4684496-scarlet?shelf=young-adult">young-adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4684496-scarlet?shelf=time-travellig">time-travellig</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4684496-scarlet?shelf=reincarnation">reincarnation</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4684496-scarlet?shelf=disappointed">disappointed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4684496-scarlet?shelf=love-triangle">love-triangle</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4684496-scarlet?shelf=not-my-cup-of-tea">not-my-cup-of-tea</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer139712323" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6169366113634085693">THANK YOU GOD, I FINISHED IT!!!<br/><b>This book sucks terribly.</b><br/>Fallen and Torment were both really good books and I found the series got a little boring, predictable and disappointing.<br/><br/>Everything in this book got so confusing:<br/>1. It has no plot at all!<br/>2. Time traveling was literally so confusing.<br/>3. Luce is dumbass: what on earth is she searching for?<br/>4. How does Daniel keep changing his appearance in almost each past life? He´s immortal after all. He doesn´t die!<br/>5. Why do all the other fallen angels alway</span>
  <span id="freeText6169366113634085693" style="display:none">THANK YOU GOD, I FINISHED IT!!!<br /><b>This book sucks terribly.</b><br />Fallen and Torment were both really good books and I found the series got a little boring, predictable and disappointing.<br /><br />Everything in this book got so confusing:<br />1. It has no plot at all!<br />2. Time traveling was literally so confusing.<br />3. Luce is dumbass: what on earth is she searching for?<br />4. How does Daniel keep changing his appearance in almost each past life? He´s immortal after all. He doesn´t die!<br />5. Why do all the other fallen angels always hang around Daniel and Luce in each life? <br />6. All the characters are doing nothing except wandering from one era to other.<br />7. My biggest disappointment (both with this book and the last) was the lack of Cam.<br /><br />Passion was 420 pages of torture . I don't know anything more about Luce and Daniel than I did in the last book.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="6169366113634085693" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


